line=57 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=88.92,577.52,538.78,588.43           :    Independent of this basic tense/aspect paradigm, there are three distinct classes of complex verbal con-
line=58 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.12 bbox=72.0,563.96,538.96,574.87:structions that will concern us in this paper. These constructions all superficially consist of the structure V1
line=59 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.12 bbox=72.0,550.4,317.37,561.31 :followed by V2, where  only V2 inflects for tense/aspect.

