line=61 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=72.0,499.64,538.73,510.55                   :In these constructions, the inflecting ‘light’ verb (here typically instantiated by the verb ‘tell’) combines
line=62 fonts=F0-10.9,F4-8.0 iscore=0.35 bbox=72.0,486.08,520.55,498.01:with an infinitive or gerund which bears a case marker identical to those found on nominal arguments.^{4}
