line=77 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=88.92,227.12,538.7,238.03            :    A number  of different case markers are theoretically possible here, depending on the final predicate.
line=78 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.05 bbox=72.0,213.56,538.68,224.47:While  the case marker used on the V1 infinitive in the case of ‘tell’ is the accusative one; the case-marker
line=79 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.15 bbox=72.0,200.0,538.74,210.91 :when  the V2 consists of ‘force do’ seems to be subject to variation with little apparent difference in meaning.
line=80 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.11 bbox=72.0,186.44,538.85,197.35:Crucially, when we come  to describing the syntactic properties of this construction, the actual choice of case
line=81 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.12 bbox=72.0,172.88,285.75,183.79:marker will not affect the behaviour we examine.

