line=355 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=88.92,163.64,538.95,174.55           :    The three distinct diagnostics we have examined here provide clear and unambiguous evidence for the
line=356 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.05 bbox=72.0,150.08,538.91,160.99:difference between our first two types (the ‘result’ and ‘let’ types) on the one hand, and the ‘tell’ type on
line=357 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.20 bbox=72.0,136.52,538.78,147.43:the other. Light verb constructions of the former type are monoclausal from the point of view of agreement,
line=358 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.22 bbox=72.0,122.96,509.62,133.87:control and anaphora; constructions of the latter type are biclausal according to all those diagnostics.

