doc_id=118 page=11 block_id=11-4 bbox=72.0,460.4,538.89,511.99 label=bbtb 414 417
line=414 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=72.0,501.08,538.89,511.99            :Under  a neo-Davidsonian semantic representation (Davidson 1967, Higginbotham  1985, Parsons 1990), ev-
line=415 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.07 bbox=72.0,487.52,538.73,498.43:ery verb contains an event position in its theta-grid, available for modification and theta-binding. Further,
line=416 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.31 bbox=72.0,473.96,538.61,484.87:thematic roles are represented as separate relations connecting the event to an individual. See the represen-
line=417 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.12 bbox=72.0,460.4,231.13,471.31 :tation of the simple sentence in (28).

