line=455 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.33 bbox=72.0,531.08,538.64,541.99                       :individuals in their own right; this does not mean that ‘apple’ is anything other than an ordinary individual
line=456 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.11 bbox=72.0,517.52,538.92,528.43                       :within the semantics.  Similarly, the macro-event corresponding to a predication is just an event which
line=457 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.20 bbox=72.0,503.96,538.41,514.87                       :happens  to have sub-parts. For some linguistic purposes (anchoring to tense, adverbs and intersentential
