line=658 fonts=F0-10.9 bbox=88.92,420.44,538.81,431.35                                   :    Because  of the productive and essentially syntactic nature of our solution, we actually predict these
line=659 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.24 bbox=72.0,406.88,538.92,417.79                        :examples  to exist, once we allow for the possibility of a little v that is equivalent to a ‘raising’ head in
