line=778 fonts=F0-10.9,F5-10.9 iscore=0.00 bbox=88.92,758.12,538.98,769.03      :    Under this view, the V2 verb liya ‘take’ is the spell-out of the head which is base generated in V and
line=779 fonts=F0-10.9,F5-10.9,F9-6.0 iscore=0.24 bbox=72.0,744.68,538.91,755.59:moves  up to v, while the V1 verb lık^{h} ‘write’ is base generated under R. Under the view of compositional
