line=890 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.22 bbox=72.0,224.0,538.78,234.91        :the functional complex. The  result type light verb, on the other hand, only optionally instantiates v (but
line=891 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.20 bbox=72.0,210.44,538.66,221.35       :always instantiates V), so that it is possible to stack another light verb on top. To put it more concretely,
line=892 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.30 bbox=72.0,197.0,539.07,207.91        :while we  would expect to find the ‘let’ light verb as the last predicative member of a verbal complex, we
line=893 fonts=F0-10.9 iscore=0.32 bbox=72.0,183.44,539.05,194.35       :would  not expect the opposite, i.e., a V1 in the oblique infinitive form, a V2 in the bare form followed by a
line=894 fonts=F0-10.9,F4-8.0 iscore=0.27 bbox=72.0,169.88,448.31,181.81:tensed V3. Once  again, this prediction is borne out and an example is shown in (59).^{18}

